sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor Officer as Club Officer
  participant UI as Web App UI
  participant PairingSvc as Pairing Service
  participant ScoreSvc as Compatibility Engine
  participant DB as Data Store
  actor Mentee
  actor Mentor
  participant MsgSvc as Messaging Service
  participant CheckInSvc as Check-In Service
  participant Analytics as Analytics Aggregator

  Officer->>UI: Open Pairing Manager
  UI->>PairingSvc: Submit mentee_id + mentor_id
  PairingSvc->>ScoreSvc: Request compatibility score
  ScoreSvc->>DB: Read profiles and history
  DB-->>ScoreSvc: Profile attributes
  ScoreSvc-->>PairingSvc: score + confidence + factors
  PairingSvc->>DB: Create pairing(status=active)
  PairingSvc-->>UI: Pairing created

  UI-->>Mentee: Pairing notification
  UI-->>Mentor: Pairing notification

  Mentee->>UI: Send first message
  UI->>MsgSvc: create_message(pairing_id)
  MsgSvc->>DB: Insert message
  MsgSvc-->>Mentor: New message event

  Mentor->>UI: Submit first check-in feedback
  Mentee->>UI: Submit reflection
  UI->>CheckInSvc: create_check_in + survey
  CheckInSvc->>DB: Insert check_in and survey_response
  CheckInSvc->>Analytics: Trigger metric refresh
  Analytics->>DB: Update analytics_snapshot
  Analytics-->>UI: Dashboard KPI update
